	('Get out','Cút đi','00:16:13.650','00:16:14.170','life-diary-animated-9'),
	('My family doesn\'t have a freak daughter like you','Gia đình tôi không có cô con gái quái dị như bạn','00:16:14.470','00:16:16.910','life-diary-animated-9'),
