	('On the contrary, she showed an innocent smile that was too ignorant for the situation','Ngược lại, cô ấy nở một nụ cười ngây thơ, quá ngây thơ cho tình huống này','00:03:23.290','00:03:28.530','life-diary-animated-12'),
	('Oh, sorry, sir','Ồ, xin lỗi ngài','00:03:29.030','00:03:30.390','life-diary-animated-12'),
	('I was careless','Tôi đã bất cẩn','00:03:30.570','00:03:31.430','life-diary-animated-12'),
	('Let me fix it','Để tôi sửa lại','00:03:31.850','00:03:33.030','life-diary-animated-12'),
	('What\'s with that joking attitude?','Cái thái độ đùa cợt gì thế?','00:03:33.530','00:03:34.970','life-diary-animated-12'),
	('No need to fix it','Không cần phải sửa','00:03:35.430','00:03:36.570','life-diary-animated-12'),
