	('Please','Làm ơn','00:10:42.520','00:10:43.100','life-diary-animated-19'),
	('Mia, how did you turn out like this?','Mia, sao cậu lại thành ra như thế này?','00:10:43.900','00:10:46.140','life-diary-animated-19'),
